StructureDefinition-CareConnect-DocumentReference-1

The DocumentReference resource is used to describe a document that is made available to a healthcare system.

Profile Minimum Viable Content (MVC)

The following elements are mandatory in the FHIR profile (i.e. MUST be present):

  1. status
  2. type
  3. indexed
  4. content
